node.text: I get roasted by the Roastmaster General, Jeff Ross, this Friday January 1st on a Special #GhostAdventures “Comedy Store” 10/9c on Travel Channel. During the roast Jeff unexpectedly shared this emotional ghost story.  BTW getting roasted by Jeff sucks HA! Watch it all go down this Friday!

node.title: Comedian Jeff Ross roasts Zak Bagans and tells emotional ghost story
